OL,3,CHow a Chinese filmmaker brought a
OL,4,Cforgotten British WWII tragedy back to
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FThe Chinese director Fang Li has set
OL,8,Fout to make sure that it is a story
OL,9,Fnone of us forget and in the process,
OL,10,Fhe has helped hundreds of British
OL,11,Ffamilies trace a key part of their
OL,12,Fhistory.
OL,14,FWhat started out as a professional
OL,15,Fcuriosity for Fang Li, became a
OL,16,Fproject that spanned the world,
OL,17,Fcreating what he describes as his
OL,18,F"greatest life work".
