OL,3,CHow a Chinese filmmaker brought a
OL,4,Cforgotten British WWII tragedy back to
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FThe Sinking of the Lisbon Maru will be
OL,8,Freleased in UK cinemas in March after
OL,9,Fsecuring a British distributor. It was
OL,10,Freleased in China this summer and
OL,11,Fproved a box office hit.
OL,13,FSeven years ago, while filming on an
OL,14,Fisland off the coast of eastern China,
OL,15,FFang Li learned about a Japanese
OL,16,Fprisoner of war transport ship called
OL,17,Fthe Lisbon Maru which had sunk in
OL,18,Fnearby waters in 1942.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
