OL,3,CHow a Chinese filmmaker brought a
OL,4,Cforgotten British WWII tragedy back to
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FLocal fisherman had helped rescue
OL,8,Fhundreds of British soldiers who the
OL,9,FJapanese had left for dead. They even
OL,10,Fopened fire on those who fell
OL,11,Foverboard.
OL,13,FPriding himself on knowing a lot about
OL,14,Fhistory and World War Two in the Asia
OL,15,FPacific, Fang Li had never heard the
OL,16,Fstory and put together a team to try
OL,17,Fto find the wreckage.
OL,19,FIt took several attempts, but he
OL,20,Feventually produced a sonar image of
OL,21,Fthe sunken Lisbon Maru.
