OL,7,FThat ended up being just beginning, as
OL,8,Fhe thought about the 820 men who died
OL,9,Fon the ship, and the 1,000 who
OL,10,Fsurvived.
OL,12,FWho were they, what happened to them,
OL,13,Fwhere were they now, and could he find
OL,14,Ftheir relatives?
OL,16,FIn 2018, he paid for full page ads to
OL,17,Fbe placed in several British
OL,18,Fnewspapers, beginning his search for
OL,19,Fthe families of the soldiers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
