OL,7,FFrom that search and with the help of
OL,8,Fthe Royal British Legion, he managed
OL,9,Fto track down what were believed to be
OL,10,Fthe last living survivors.
OL,12,FBrian Morley and William Benningfield
OL,13,Fboth died before the film was
OL,14,Fcompleted, but their testimony, still
OL,15,Fso clear after all these years, was
OL,16,Fcrucial to what Fang Li was able to
OL,17,Fproduce.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
