OL,3,CHow a Chinese filmmaker brought a
OL,4,Cforgotten British WWII tragedy back to
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FAlthough glad to have been able to
OL,8,Fmeet them, and share their stories,
OL,9,FFang felt regret for not having
OL,10,Fstarted the project sooner.
OL,12,FSeveral families also got in touch and
OL,13,Fagreed to share what they knew, and
OL,14,Fletters or photographs sent by their
OL,15,Floved ones who had been on board.
OL,17,FUsing animation and recorded testimony
OL,18,Ffrom the Imperial War Museum, Fang Li
OL,19,Fpieced together the events of the
OL,20,Ffirst few days of October 1942, to re-
OL,21,Fcreate the journey of the Lisbon Maru.
