OL,7,FDetailing the appalling conditions
OL,8,Fendured by the British POWs and the
OL,9,Fterrifying moment when the vessel was
OL,10,Fstruck by torpedoes.
OL,12,FThe ship was unmarked, and an American
OL,13,Fsubmarine mistook it for a regular
OL,14,FJapanese transport ship.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
