OL,3,CHow a Chinese filmmaker brought a
OL,4,Cforgotten British WWII tragedy back to
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FBefore he passed away, naval officer
OL,8,FJack Hughieson gave his oral testimony
OL,9,Fto the Imperial War Museum and his
OL,10,Fvoice appears in the film talking
OL,11,Fabout the two days he survived in the
OL,12,Fwater before he was rescued by Chinese
OL,13,Ffishermen.
OL,15,FIt is a harrowing and moving account
OL,16,Fthat shows the incredible strength of
OL,17,Fcharacter of the men of that time.
OL,19,FThe film has been entered for the
OL,20,FOscars and the BAFTAs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
