OL,3,CHow a Chinese filmmaker brought a
OL,4,Cforgotten British WWII tragedy back to
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FFang Li has already been awarded
OL,8,Fseveral accolades in China, but he
OL,9,Fsays the real prize has been bring the
OL,10,Ffamilies of the Lisbon Maru POWs
OL,11,Ftogether.
OL,13,FIt is thanks to his determination that
OL,14,Fone of Britain's largest losses of
OL,15,Flife at sea has been brought to the
OL,16,Fbig screen.
